title: KMSpico v10.2.0 fixed
description:
KMSpico v10.2.0 

Activator for Windows and Office

- Requirements: .NET 4.0 or Windows 8/8.1/10/2012/2016.

- Activate:
Windows Vista Bussines/Enterprise
Windows 7 Professional/Enterprise
Windows 8/8.1/10 All
Office 2010/2013/2016
Windows Server 2008/2008R2/2012/2012R2/2016 (Theorically)


Run KMSpico_setup.exe
Install it.
(Optional) Create a tokens backup with the buttom: Create.
Press the Red Button.
Done.


Change Log
v10.2.0
- Fixed bugs with Office 2010 activation in W8.1/W10.
- Add feature to remove the KMS Emulator IP address from products in W8.1/W10 after activation
